|:------|:----------------------------------|:------------------------------------------|:----------------------------------|
| close | [Phoneme i](PhonemeTable?#cldf:i) | [Phoneme 1](PhonemeTable?#cldf:1)         | [Phoneme u](PhonemeTable?#cldf:u) |
