        * ‘past.abs.nzr’
        * ‘past.act.nzr?’ 
    * ?[Morpheme neinf](MorphsetTable?#cldf:neinf) ‘infinitive / generic action nominalizer’
        * Only intransitive verbs? no also *wanumanë* 'gossip, lie' and *wajtënë* 'dance' 
    * [Morpheme ninmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:ninmlz) ‘a.nzr’
    * [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre) ‘o.nzr’
        * [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre)V[Morpheme rinmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:rinmlz)    ‘nonpast?’
        * ?? [Morpheme nnmlzpre](MorphsetTable?#cldf:nnmlzpre)V[Morpheme jpepst](MorphsetTable?#cldf:jpepst)    ‘past?’
    * [Morpheme sapepfv](MorphsetTable?#cldf:sapepfv) ‘abs.nzr’ (contrast with ‑jpë )
    * [Morpheme toponmlz](MorphsetTable?#cldf:toponmlz) ‘circ.nzr’
