## Person prefixes {#sec:verbperson}


<a id='tab:verbprefixes'></a><div class='caption table' id='tab:verbprefixes'>Person marking prefixes on verbs</div>

|                                  | <span class=""smallcaps"">intr</span>     | <span class=""smallcaps"">tr</span>       |
|:---------------------------------|:----------------------------------------|:----------------------------------------|
| <span class=""smallcaps"">1</span> | [Morpheme u1](MorphsetTable?#cldf:u1)   | [Morpheme u1](MorphsetTable?#cldf:u1)   |
